revision.text:
The '''2008 French Road Cycling Cup''' is the seventeenth edition of the [[French Road Cycling Cup]]. It started on February 24 with the [[Tour du Haut Var]] and finished on October 9 with [[Paris–Bourges]]. [[Jérôme Pineau]] of {{ct|EUC|2008}} won the overall competition, despite not winning any of the races.

