The '''Bahamas Davis Cup team''' represents the [[Bahamas]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Bahamas Lawn Tennis Association]].
The Bahamas currently compete in the Americas Zone of Group II. They reached the World Group Play-offs in [[1993 Davis Cup|1993]].
==History== The Bahamas competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1989 Davis Cup|1989]]. Bahamian players previously competed on the Caribbean/West Indies team.
