{{Distinguish|Central Hockey League (1963–84) Rookie of the Year}} {{Infobox ice hockey award |name = CHL Rookie of the Year Award |image = CHL Rookie of the Year.jpg |alt = |established= 1988 |disestablished= |holder = [[Alexis Lafrenière]] |awarded = Annually to the top rookie in the Canadian Hockey League }}
The '''CHL Rookie of the Year Award''' is given out annually to the top rookie in the [[Canadian Hockey League]]. It is chosen from the winners of; the [[Emms Family Award]] (OHL Rookie of the Year), the [[Jim Piggott Memorial Trophy]] (WHL Rookie of the Year), and the [[RDS Cup]] (QMJHL Rookie of the Year).
