'''Mazarea Dina FC''' ({{Lang-arz|مزارع دينا}}) is an [[Egypt]]ian [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Cairo]]. It was founded under the name '''Ittihad Othman''' ({{Lang-ar|اتحاد عثمان}}), and was changed to the current name in 1998.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://forum.kooora.com/?t=31629615 |accessdate=October 20, 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112064701/http://forum.kooora.com/?t=31629615 |archivedate=January 12, 2015|title=المـوسـوعة الشـامـلة والـتـاريخية للـدوري المـصــــري الـممـتــاز}}</ref>
